esis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35870,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/28\/baqarah-ayat-al-kursi\/","url_meta":{"origin":3870,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Al-Baqarah is peak of the Book of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEverything has a summit, and the summit of the Quran is Surat al-Baqarah. It contains a verse which is the chief of the Quran, the verse of the Throne.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2878 Grade: Hasan li\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35872,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/28\/shaytan-out-of-house\/","url_meta":{"origin":3870,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Surat al-Baqarah keeps Satan out of home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, everything has a summit and the summit of the Quran is Surat al-Baqarah. Whoever recites it in his house at night, Satan will not enter his house for three nights. Whoever recites it during\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/q